These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, grapefruit, grapes, nectarine
4 different pets are kept: horse, hedgehog, goldfish, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, tram, roller, car
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person driving the car is the owner of the horse##1
3. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person driving the roller and the person eating grapefruit##2
6. the person driving the tram is the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapes | nectarine  | grapefruit | pepper  |
| Pet         | rabbit    | hedgehog  | horse       | goldfish     |
| Transport   | roller     | bike | car       | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, traveling, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, satire, epic, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, cycling, biathlon, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching crime movies and the person who's hobby is singing##2
5. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | puzzles | cooking    | singing  | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | horror  | satire   | epic    |
| Sport         | cycling | rugby | weightlifting | biathlon      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, coffee, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, sudoku, chess, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, punk, ambient, pop
1. the fan of punk is between the fan of pop and the person drinking cola##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the fan of techno##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
6. the fan of techno is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | cola | hot-chocolate         | soy-milk   | coffee    |
| Hobby         | sudoku | board-games | magic-tricks | chess |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | punk        | pop      | techno   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, thai, nigerian, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, volleyball, skiing, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, bike, boat
1. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the boat and the pakistani##2
3. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the nigerian is on the right of the british##1
6. the person driving the boat is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani        | thai   | british | nigerian |
| Sport         | skiing | parkour | volleyball    | water-polo |
| Transport     | bike       | jet-ski     | boat       | van    |

