.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, mirinda, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, card-games, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, surfing, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water      | sprite       | mirinda   |
| Hobby      | cooking   | hiking  | dancing | card-games     |
| Sport      | surfing     | water-polo | swimming        | climbing |

