.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, cabbage, pear
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, cooking, card-games, board-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, sailing, weightlifting, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
6. the person eating carrot is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating cabbage##2
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | cabbage | carrot  | artichoke | pear      |
| Hobby   | card-games  | board-games  | video-games | cooking |
| Sport   | volleyball | surfing | sailing | weightlifting     |

