.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cabbage, orange, plum
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, crime, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, weightlifting, water-polo, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person eating orange is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person eating cabbage is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
7. the person eating plum is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | orange  | cabbage    | plum | cauliflower  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | western       | crime        | thriller    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | lacrosse | swimming  | water-polo |

