.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, puzzles, traveling, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, drama, sports
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, mouse, cat
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is between the owner of the cat and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking  | puzzles | traveling | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | sports | mystery   | drama         |
| Pet           | chinchilla | mouse  | fish   | cat      |

