.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, orange, pineapple, peach
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, card-games, skydiving, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, dubstep, gospel, classical
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of classical##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person eating cranberry##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person eating orange##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person eating orange##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating peach##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the fan of gospel and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | peach  | cranberry    | pineapple | orange       |
| Hobby         | board-games | card-games | hiking  | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | classical      | dubstep  | r&b     |

