2. the person eating apricot is on the far left##1
3. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating artichoke and the person who's hobby is singing##2
4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
7. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person watching superhero movies is the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
