.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, pineapple, cherry, lettuce
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, singing, dancing, photography
4 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, horse, goldfish
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the owner of the horse is the person eating pineapple##1
3. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the owner of the turtle and the person eating lettuce##2
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the owner of the fish##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | lettuce  | cherry | plum | pineapple     |
| Hobby   | drawing | dancing   | photography  | singing    |
| Pet     | fish        | goldfish       | turtle      | horse |

