4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
