.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, chef, security-guard, accountant
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, spy, family, zombie
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, van, tram, roller
1. the person watching drama movies is the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the tram is the security-guard##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the police-officer##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the van is between the person watching family movies and the security-guard##2
6. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the van is the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | chef | accountant | security-guard    | police-officer   |
| Movie-Genre   | family      | spy   | zombie | drama |
| Transport     | boat     | van       | tram        | roller    |

