.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, lemonade, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, folk, punk, metal
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, polish, colombian, turkish
1. the fan of d&b is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking lemonade and the polish##2
3. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of folk##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is between the fan of punk and the turkish##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the egyptian is between the colombian and the fan of metal##2
7. the fan of d&b is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up | lemonade | milk   | tea |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | folk    | punk   | metal     |
| Nationality   | turkish  | colombian | egyptian | polish   |

