3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating pear##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite    | milk | lemonade           | 7up |
| Food       | plum | pear    | cabbage          | apricot   |
| Sport      | parkour  | basketball   | golf | sailing  |

