4. the person drinking juice is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching spy movies##2
5. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the owner of the dog is between the person drinking iced-tea and the owner of the rabbit##2
7. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
