3. the teacher is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the car is the videographer##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | teacher        | videographer  | entrepreneur | security-guard   |
| Sport       | baseball | soccer | tennis    | biathlon |
| Transport   | van        | car     | skateboard       | bus      |

