.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, orange, apricot, potato
4 different pets are kept: pony, turtle, guinea-pig, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, scooter, tram, van
1. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the van is the owner of the rat##1
6. the owner of the turtle is between the person eating potato and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | potato | orange | pineapple | apricot |
| Pet         | pony       | turtle     | guinea-pig   | rat   |
| Transport   | bus | scooter | tram | van |

 